02:33.480 --> 02:34.970
<i>[woman] Good morning,</i>
<i>Ms. Jones.</i>

02:35.170 --> 02:37.110
<i>This is the wake-up call</i>
<i>you requested.</i>

02:46.870 --> 02:48.860
