02:58.230 --> 03:00.870
- Dada! Yay, yay!
- Hey.

03:01.070 --> 03:02.660
Hey.

03:02.860 --> 03:04.540
- Good morning, beautiful.
- Oh, yeah.

03:04.740 --> 03:07.830
- Good morning, good morning.
- Hi. Mm.

03:08.030 --> 03:09.540
You want any breakfast?

03:09.740 --> 03:11.300
Oh, yeah? Uh...

03:11.500 --> 03:13.150
No, I should get showered
and get going.

03:14.360 --> 03:16.010
What time do you think
you'll be back?

03:16.210 --> 03:18.720
[groans] If it goes well...

03:18.920 --> 03:22.270
[sighs] I don't know,
in time for dinner.

03:22.460 --> 03:25.480
- And if doesn't?
- [sighs]

03:25.680 --> 03:28.480
Well, if it doesn't,
then it's gonna be a long night.

03:28.680 --> 03:30.650
- All right.
- All right.

