♪ <i>Love is the drug</i>
<i>got a hook on me</i> ♪

03:34.770 --> 03:38.870
♪ <i>Oh, catch that buzz</i> ♪

03:39.060 --> 03:42.490
♪ <i>Love is the drug</i>
<i>I'm thinking of</i> ♪

